Final Summary

This project demonstrates an industry-standard sports analytics workflow from raw data ingestion through feature engineering, model training, and evaluation. It highlights the value of fatigue modeling while maintaining scientific honesty about its limitations. The project showcases both technical machine learning skill and applied domain understanding, making it a strong portfolio artifact for data science and sports analytics roles.